-You should be in a sideshow!

1000
01:15:18,400 --> 01:15:19,269
Go on! Get out of here!

1001
01:15:19,480 --> 01:15:20,559
Come on, Lenore.
We don't need this shit!

1002
01:15:20,800 --> 01:15:21,960
Get out of here!

1003
01:15:23,680 --> 01:15:25,820
-You retard.
